entry.title: Azure-Samples/todo-python-mongo-swa-func
entry.summary: A complete ToDo application that includes everything you need to build, deploy, and monitor an Azure solution. This application uses the Azure Developer CLI (azd) to get you up and running on Azure quickly using React.js for the Web application, Python for the API and Azure Cosmos DB API for MongoDB for storage.
